PROBLEM: I/P= n=35       (perfect sqrt(35) is not present)
         O/P= 0
         
         I/P= n=49       (sqrt(49)=7)
         O/P= 1
         
SOLUTION:

long long int isPerfectSquare(long long int n){
        
        for(int i=1;i*i<=n;i++){
            if((i*i)==n){
                return 1;
            }
        }
        return 0;
    }
